<seg function="incipit"><lb n="1"/>vāṉiṭu villiṉ varalaṟiyā vāymaiyāṟ 
kāṉilan tōyāk kaṭavuḷai – yāṉilañ
ceṉṉi yuṟavaṇaṅkic cērtumem muḷḷattu
muṉṉi yavaimuṭika veṉṟu ௳ 1 ௳ <note xml:lang="en">Found in the <title xml:lang="ta">Uraippāyiram</title> of the 1921 edition, p. 6, as <foreign xml:lang="ta">kaṭavuḷ vāḻttu</foreign> in the <term xml:lang="ta">Kaḻakam</term> edition, p.1, and in the <term xml:lang="ta">Caracuvatimakāl</term> edition, p. 12.</note></seg> 
veḷḷāṉ marapukku vētameṉa<lb n="2"/>c cāṉṟōrka
ḷellāruṅ kūṭi yeṭutturaittuc – collāynta
nālaṭi ṉāṉūṟu naṉkiṉitā meṉmaṉattē
cīlamuṭa ṉiṟkavē ceppu ௳ 2 ௳ <note xml:lang="en">Found in the <term xml:lang="ta">Caracuvatimakāl</term> edition, p. 1 (together with 2 further verses).</note>
maṉṉaṉ vaḻutiyarkōṉ vaikaip pe<lb n="3"/>yarāṟṟi
leṇṇi yirunāṉkō rāyiravar – uṉṉi 
yeḻutiyiṭu mēṭṭi letirē naṭanta
paḻutilā nālaṭiyaip pār ௳ 3 ௳ <note xml:lang="en">Found in the <title xml:lang="ta">Varalāṟu</title> of the 1921 edition, p. 1.</note>
paraṅkuṉ ṟorupaka mapparam paḷḷi
yiruṅkuṉṟam pērā<lb n="4"/>cai yāṉai – yaruṅkuṉṟa
meṉṟeṭṭu veṟpu meṭuttiyampa vallārkkuc
ceṉṟeṭṭu mōviraivit tīṅku ௳ 4 ௳
eṇperuṅ kuṉṟat teṇṇāyira muṉivar
paṇporuntap pāṭiyapā <lb n="5"/>ṉāṉūṟun taṇporunta
nīretirkoṇ ṭōṭutalāl nīṉṟicaip pāmeṉṟitaṉaip
pāretir koṇṭārpayaṉaip parattu ௳ 5 ௳   
ciṟappuppāyiram muṟṟum ௳ <seg function="blessing">civappiramaṇiyakaṭāṣcam</seg>
    
    <pb facs="6" n="1v"/><note xml:lang="en">blank</note>

     <pb facs="7" n="2r"/>
    
<seg function="incipit"><lb n="1"/>celvam nilaiyāmai ~ Aḵtāvaṉ ~ poruḷ ~ Aracaraṭci ~ yitumutalāyiṉavai celvamātali ṉaḵtunilaiyillaiyeṉpatu ~ Aaṟam nilaiyeṉpatu paṟṟi ivai poruḷuṭaṉ muyaṅkiya teṉka kūṟiṉa ‡‡ - 
Arucuvai yuṇṭi ~ <lb n="2"/>yamarntillā ḷūṭṭa ~ 
maṟucikai nīkkiyuṇ ṭākum ~ vaṟiṉārāyc 
ceṉṟirappa rōriṭattiṟ kēṟeṉil celvamoṉ 
ṟuṇṭāka vaikkappāṟ ṟaṉṟu ௳ Eṉṟatu ௳</seg>
Aṟucuvaiyum poruntiya vuṇṭiyai virumpi maṉaiyā<lb n="3"/>ḷuṭṭa muṟcikai nīkkip piṟcikaiyuṇṭāru matarittiraṇpañariṭattiṟ poykkūḻiṉai yirapparākalē celvattai niṉaiyuṇṭeṉṟu niṉaikkappaṭāteṉṟavāṟu ~ Aṟucuvai titittal ~ puḷittal ~ kūrt<lb n="4"/>tal ~ tuvarttal ~ kārttal ~ kaittala ~ Aṟuvakai ~ maṟucikaiyeṉṟatu ~ muṟcikai nīkkip piṟacikai yuṇpateṉa valaika vaḻakkam ~ kūḻaviṉaippeyar ௳ 
    
            <seg function="explicit"><pb facs="137" n="67r"/>
<lb n="4"/>kaṇmūṉ ṟuṭaiyāṉuṅ kākkaiyum paiyaravu
meṉṉīṉṟa yāyum piḻaittateṉ <lb n="5"/>– poṉṉiṉṟa
kōṅkarum peṉṉa mulaiyāy poruḷvayiṟ
pāṅkaṉuñ ceṉṟa ṉeṟi ௳ Etu ௳
talaimakaḷ pirivāṟṟāmaiyait tōḻikkuc colliyatu mūṉṟu kaṇṇiṉaiyuṭaiya civaṉum kākkaiyum paṭattaiyuṭaiya  <lb n="6"/>pāmpum yeṉṉaip petta tāyum yāṉ varuntac ceyta kuṟṟaṅkaḷ yātumillai poṉpōluṅ kōṅkarum piṉaiyotta mulaiyiṉaiyuṭaiyavaḷē poruḷ tēṭap pōṉa nāyakaṉ pōṉa vaḻiyē nammai varuttañ ce<lb n="7"/>yvateṉṟavāṟu ~ kaṇmūṉṟuṭaiya civaṉ piḻaiceytatu kāmaṉai yuruvaḻittum piṉṉaiyu mavaṉai yuṇṭākkiṉa paṭiyiṉālē ~ kākkai varuttañ ceyvitttaṟkuk kāraṇaṅ kuyil muṭṭaiyiṭāa taṉai vaḷarntuk kūvavaitantām ~ pāmpu 
    
    <pb n="67v" facs="138"/>varuttañ ceyvittaṟku kāraṇam ~ tāṉ muḻaṅkiṉa cantiraṉai cerippittuk koḷḷāmal tirumpivippatām ~ tāy varuttañ ceyvittaṟku kāraṇam ~ taṉṉaip pettu vaḷarttu varuntavaittatām ~ ye
    <lb n="2" break="no"/>ṉṟa vāṟu ௳ <g ref="#pattu"/> ~ </seg> <seg function="colophon">muṟṟum <seg function="total-chapters total-stanzas">Ākaviyal ~ 3kku ~ Atikāram – 4<g ref="#pattu"/>kku ~ veṇpā ~ 4<g ref="#nūṟu"/> ~</seg> muṭintatu ~ cittiraravutti vaṟuṭam paiṅkuṉi {mācam} – 2<g ref="#pattu"/>2 ௳ maṅkalavāram ṉāḷ Eḻuti muṭintatu ௳ Aṇaṅkuvayal cūḻumāṉa tirumēvu miṇarvillai
    <lb n="3"/>vācamē vāḻunatiṇai maliyum muttukkumaraṉ ‡ ṉa muṉmaintaṉ kantaṉoṭu cuppumayila ṉālaṭiyār cūḻ ௳ Itaṉ iyalpu ~ <persName xml:lang="ta" role="scribe">villavaṉ nallūril mēviya muttukumarp piḷḷaikumarāṉ kantacuvāmi</persName> ṉālaṭi<lb n="4"/>yār uraiyuṭaṉē yeḻutiṉatu ௳ <seg function="blessing">civakurukaṭāṣcamē Uṇṭākavum</seg> <seg function="blessing">civacuppiramaṇiyak kaṭavuḷ pātamē tuṇai</seg></seg>
    
